      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "If anyone is interested, since I just had to look it up: According to the <a href=\"http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/documentation/index-137868.html#orderoftags\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Javadoc spec</a> the <code>@see</code> tag comes <i>after</i> the <code>@param</code>/<code>@return</code> tags and <i>before</i> the <code>@since</code>/<code>@serial</code>/<code>@deprecated</code> tags."
