      "body" : "I recommend <code>&lt;a href=&quot;http:&#47;&#47;google.com&quot; target=&quot;_top&quot;&gt;http:&#47;&#47;google.com&lt;&#47;a&gt;.</code>  The reason for adding target=&quot;_top&quot; is because some of the generated javadoc html files make use of frames, and you probably want the navigation to affect the whole page rather than just the current frame."
