    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This creates a \"See Also\" heading containing the link, i.e.:</p>\n\n<pre><code>/**\n * @see &lt;a href=\"http://google.com\"&gt;http://google.com&lt;/a&gt;\n */\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>will render as:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p><strong>See Also:</strong><br/>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://google.com\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://google.com</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>whereas this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>/**\n * See &lt;a href=\"http://google.com\"&gt;http://google.com&lt;/a&gt;\n */\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>will create an in-line link:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>See <a href=\"http://google.com\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://google.com</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n"
  }, {
